BORAX CONSOLIDATED, Inc., Appellant, v. PACIFIC IRON & STEEL COMPANY et al., Appellees. No. 7299. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Oct. 8, 1934. Newlin & Ashburn, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellant. Walter H. Moses, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellee.

Before WILBUR, SAWTELLE, and GARRECHT, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for the respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
